<style>
  #container-myVideo {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
  }
  
  #container-myVideo iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
</style>
<main>
  <!-- slider Area Start-->
  <div class="slider-area slider-height background-color-default">
    <div class="slider-active">
      <!-- Single Slider -->
      <div class="single-slider">
        <div class="slider-cap-wrapper">
          <div class="hero__img">
            <img src="<%= image_path('hero_img.jpg') %>" alt=""  data-animation="fadeInRight" data-transition-duration="5s">
          </div>
          <div class="hero__caption">
            <h1 data-animation="fadeInLeft" data-delay="1s" 
              style="font-style: italic; font-size: 3.2rem;">
              Try flying to know <br/>
              how far you can fly
            </h1>
            <p data-animation="fadeInLeft" data-delay="1.3s" style="font-size: 1.3rem;">
              Istart-up là sân chơi dành cho những người có cùng đam mê khởi nghiệp
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- slider Area End-->
  <div class="wantToWork-area w-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12" id="container-myVideo">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yi6Ip_ru5w0" frameborder="0" 
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Want To Work Start -->
  <div class="wantToWork-area w-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end">
        <div class="col-xl-5 col-lg-7 col-md-8">
          <div class="wantToWork-caption">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
              With the continuous development and diversity of current fields such as 
              e-commerce, tourism and hotels... Istart-up Club is opened with the 
              general purpose of creating a common playground for young students who 
              have a passion for creativity in the startup industry. Moreover, we would 
              like to link from here to the solidarity between the other major students, and the 
              connection of different clubs in the same school. As Larry Page - 
              Co-founder of Google once said: "You don't need a company with 100 employees 
              to develop an idea." Whether an idea can develop or not, it depends entirely on 
              ourselves. Let's create an enthusiastic youth with the dream of starting a 
              career in your desired field
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-7 col-lg-5 col-md-4">
          <div class="wantToWork-btn f-right">
            <a href="<%= about_path %>" class="btn btn-ans">Details about us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Want To Work End -->
  <!-- Want To Work Start -->
  <%= render partial: 'home/want_to_contact' %>
  <!-- Want To Work End -->
</main>
